Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.77,1:31:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在很久以前
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.52,1:31:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不知多久以前
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.11,1:31:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟多久了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.66,1:32:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知從何時起…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.00,1:32:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就存在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.13,1:32:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我找你找了好久
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.59,1:32:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,找了600年
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.55,1:32:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你名字改成友魚了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.43,1:32:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,名字改回來後真難找
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.18,1:32:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我問你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.98,1:32:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是幫自己取了名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.52,1:32:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡有我們的故事 對吧 友有
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.83,1:32:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,犬…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.87,1:32:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你還拿著那把獨角仙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.75,1:32:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還能彈嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.59,1:32:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.81,1:33:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯耶
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.77,1:33:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.11,1:33:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你都沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.98,1:33:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.44,1:33:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.53,1:33:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我要繼續囉
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.67,1:33:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,犬王
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.13,1:33:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,友有
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.92,1:33:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,犬王
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.51,1:33:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,友有
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.09,1:33:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,犬王
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.05,1:33:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,友有
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.97,1:33:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,犬王！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.97,1:33:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,友有！
